        <h1 class="article-title">An address by Opposition Leader Anthony Albanese</h1>
    <div class="article-intro intro-text">
      <p>Opposition Leader Anthony Albanese addressed&nbsp;the Lowy Institute on how a Labor government would deliver national security in a complex world.</p>

    </div>

          <div class="article-authors">
        By
        <span>
                      <a href="/people/contributor/bio/anthony-albanese">
              Anthony Albanese
            </a>
                  </span>
      </div>
    
    <div class="article-published-date">4 March 2022</div>
    </div>
  </div>



